moji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nagger,拎20分讀hkcc都讀到喊<br />\n堆人好勁，好彩我都有offer<br />\n覺得自己一般既就cccu，聽lecturer講間野咩人都有<br />\ncccu起碼唔使比人屈機先"},{"pid":"e707493835da4103378a7691a0d4981197403a46","tid":237404,"uid":14449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T09:35:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>社科CCCU 其他HKCC<br />\n原因都係好grade d同易d升返</blockquote><br />\ncccu pam好似好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n識唔識louis?"},{"pid":"f22693b298520d3dbafcceac227ae0adf0c85982","tid":237404,"uid":122611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T16:51:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>hkcc <br />\ncccu 教啲野難啲<br />\n利申 cccu</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個人覺得教啲野越難代表你學啲野越多 到升ugc要interview就會屈機<br />\n利申cccu interview屈機入左三大"},{"pid":"cbb717c44a16c46213e1d24123e5d4a28c25e05e","tid":237404,"uid":122611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T17:03:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>社科CCCU 其他HKCC<br />\n原因都係好grade d同易d升返</blockquote><br />\ncccu pam好似好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n識唔識louis?</blockquote><br />\nlouis走左啦~雖然佢係派grade但聽佢上堂真心悶。但其實全部老師都派grade架啦，唔只louis一個<br />\n其實pam唔勁 但教啲野相對深 所以屈機<br />\n有個老師叫Raymond整左套master程度既教材黎教 勁detail 但其實唔深 花多小小時間睇就得 靠呢套野去interview又好升上去讀又好 基本上輕鬆1st hon<br />\n雖然係深 但so far我又冇聽過有人話唔識 我諗都只係相對chur啲姐<br />\n<br />\n我覺得cccu既社科一定係比hkcc好 睇cccu開幾多唔同科幾專門化就知 其他科就唔知了"},{"pid":"689e8aab5f65e0d3888752b396fd04077e507481","tid":237404,"uid":120451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T15:15:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"11a3b94d1476f3854f3871c63abbd637357593ef","tid":237404,"uid":22628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T13:28:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n推呀推"},{"pid":"9a7d629397740027911d4aac4484272775783a84","tid":2374